    { "type": "textarea",     "id": "barrier_body_2",  "label": "Paragraph 2", "default": "When it's compromised, your skin reacts. Redness, breakouts, sensitivity, and dehydration are often symptoms of a barrier issue — not separate problems." },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Active Ingredient Guide"
    },
    { "type": "text",     "id": "actives_eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow",    "default": "Your guide" },
    { "type": "text",     "id": "actives_heading", "label": "Heading",    "default": "AM, PM, and layering rules." },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "actives_intro",   "label": "Intro text", "default": "Not all actives can be used at the same time. This guide explains when to apply each ingredient and what to avoid layering together." },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "FAQ"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "faq_eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow", "default": "Questions" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "faq_title",   "label": "Heading", "default": "Ingredient FAQ" },
    {
